{"article_id":"kUNqSsV4PgaUDXlF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"EXCLUSIVE :","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Highly classified Hillary Clinton emails","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"that the intelligence community and State Department recently deemed too damaging to national security to release","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"contain \" operational intelligence \"","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"- and their presence on the unsecure , personal email system jeopardized \" sources , methods and lives , \"","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"a U.S. government official","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"who has reviewed the documents","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"told Fox News .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"The official ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"who was not authorized to speak on the record","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"and was limited in discussing the contents","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"because of their highly classified nature ,","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"was referring to the 22 \" TOP SECRET \" emails","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"the State Department announced Friday","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"it could not release in any form , even with entire sections redacted .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"The announcement fueled criticism of Clinton ' s handling of highly sensitive information while secretary of state ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"even as the Clinton campaign continued to downplay the matter as the product of an interagency dispute over classification .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"But the U.S. government official ' s description provides confirmation","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"that the emails contained closely held government secrets .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"\" Operational intelligence \" can be real-time information about intelligence collection , sources and the movement of assets .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"The official emphasized","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"that the \" TOP SECRET \" documents were sent over an extended period of time","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"-- from shortly after the server 's 2009 installation until early 2013","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"when Clinton stepped down as secretary of state .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Separately , Rep. Mike Pompeo , R-Kan. ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"who sits on the House intelligence committee ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"the former secretary of state , senator , and Yale-trained lawyer had to know","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"what she was dealing with .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"`` There is no way","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"that someone , a senior government official","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"who has been handling classified information for a good chunk of their adult life ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"could not have known","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"that this information ought to be classified ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"whether it was marked or not , \"","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"`` Anyone with the capacity","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"to read","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"and an understanding of American national security , an 8th grade reading level or above ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"would understand","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"that the release of this information or the potential breach of a non-secure system presented risk to American national security . ''","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Pompeo also suggested","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"the military and intelligence communities have had to change operations ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"because the Clinton server could have been compromised by a third party .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"\" Anytime our national security team determines","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that there 's a potential breach ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that is information","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"that might potentially have fallen into the hands of the Iranians , or the Russians , or the Chinese , or just hackers ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"that they begin to operate in a manner","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"that assumes","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"that information has in fact gotten out , \"","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Pompeo said .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"On ABC 's \" This Week \" on Sunday , one day before the Iowa caucuses , Clinton claimed ignorance on the sensitivity of the materials","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"and stressed","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"that they weren ' t marked .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"`` There is no classified marked information on those emails","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"sent or received by me , ''","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"she said ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"adding","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"that \" Republicans are going to continue to use it","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"[ to ] beat up on me . \"","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Clinton was pressed in the same ABC interview on her signed 2009 non-disclosure agreement","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"which acknowledged","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"that markings are irrelevant ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"undercutting her central explanation .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"The agreement states","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"`` classified information is marked or unmarked ... including oral communications . ''","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Clinton pointed to her aides ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"saying :","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"`` When you receive information ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"of course , there has to be some markings , some indication","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"that someone down the chain had thought","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"that this was classified","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"and that was not the case . \"","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"according to national security legal experts ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"security clearance holders are required to speak up","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"when classified information is not in secure channels .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"`` Everybody","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"who has a security clearance","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"has an individual obligation","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"to protect the information , ''","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"said national security attorney Edward MacMahon Jr. ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"who represented former CIA officer Jeffrey Sterling in the high-profile leak investigation","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"regarding a New York Times reporter .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"`` Just because somebody sends it to you ...","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"you ca n't just turn a blind eye","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"and pretend","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"it never happened","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"and pretend","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"it 's unclassified information . ''","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"These rules ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"known as the Code of Federal Regulations ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"apply to U.S. government employees with security clearances","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"and state","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"there is an obligation","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"to report any possible breach by both the sender and the receiver of the information .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"The rules state :","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"`` Any person","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"who has knowledge","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"that classified information has been or may have been lost , possibly compromised or disclosed to an unauthorized person","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"shall immediately report the circumstances to an official","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"designated for this purpose . ''","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"The Clinton campaign is now calling for the 22 \" TOP SECRET \" emails to be released ,","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"but this is not entirely the State Department 's call","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"since the intelligence came from other agencies ,","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"which have final say on classification and handling .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"`` The State Department has no authority","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"to release those emails","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"and I do think","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"that Secretary Clinton most assuredly knows that , ''","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"Pompeo said .","depth":5},{"id":113,"text":"Meanwhile , the release of other emails has revealed more about the high-level exchange of classified information on personal accounts .","depth":3},{"id":114,"text":"Among the latest batch of emails","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"released by the State Department","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"is an exchange between Clinton and then-Sen. John Kerry , now secretary of state .","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"Sections are fully redacted ,","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"citing classified information","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"- and both Kerry and Clinton were using unsecured , personal accounts .","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"Further , a 2009 email","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"released to Judicial Watch","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"after a federal lawsuit","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"-- and first reported by Fox News --","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"suggests","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"the State Department 's senior manager Patrick Kennedy was trying to make it easier for Clinton to check her personal email at work ,","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"writing to Clinton aide Cheryl Mills","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"a","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"`` stand-alone separate network PC is ... [ one ] great idea . '' `` The emails show","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"that the top administrator at the State Department , Patrick Kennedy ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"who is still there","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"overseeing the response to all the inquiries about Hillary Clinton ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"was in on Hillary Clinton 's separate email network and system from the get-go , ''","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Judicial Watch President Tom Fitton said .","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"Kennedy is expected to testify this month before the Republican-led Benghazi Select Committee .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":269,"left":187,"right":268,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":0,"right":186,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":186,"left":158,"right":185,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":158,"left":154,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":151,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":149,"right":150,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":141,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":138,"right":140,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":137,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":137,"left":136,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":136,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":139,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":139,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":145,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":144,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":144,"left":8,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":9,"right":142,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":142,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":13,"right":146,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":146,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":20,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":15